s/026-offline-coaching-decision-tree-exhaustive","line":109},{"title":"../../03-decisions/011-coach-decision-log-architecture","target":"../../03-decisions/011-coach-decision-log-architecture","line":110},{"title":"../../03-decisions/020-storage-tiering-strategy","target":"../../03-decisions/020-storage-tiering-strategy","line":111},{"title":"../entities/engines/engine-coach-director","target":"../entities/engines/engine-coach-director","line":112},{"title":"../entities/adrs/adr-020-storage-tiering-strategy","target":"../entities/adrs/adr-020-storage-tiering-strategy","line":113},{"title":"../concepts/metoda-hibrida-chat-cc","target":"../concepts/metoda-hibrida-chat-cc","line":114},{"title":"../../📤_outbox/_archive/2026-05/442_LATEST_PREVIOUS_WIKI_INGEST_HANDOVER_SUB_BATCH_3_CLOSURE_CONSUMED","target":"../../📤_outbox/_archive/2026-05/442_LATEST_PREVIOUS_WIKI_INGEST_HANDOVER_SUB_BATCH_3_CLOSURE_CONSUMED","line":115},{"title":"../../📤_outbox/_archive/2026-05/443_LATEST_PREVIOUS_CALENDAR_V1_SLICE_1_DESIGN_MASTER_CONSUMED","target":"../../📤_outbox/_archive/2026-05/443_LATEST_PREVIOUS_CALENDAR_V1_SLICE_1_DESIGN_MASTER_CONSUMED","line":116},{"title":"../../📤_outbox/_archive/2026-05/444_LATEST_PREVIOUS_CALENDAR_V1_SLICE_1_5_FIX_BUNDLE_CONSUMED","target":"../../📤_outbox/_archive/2026-05/444_LATEST_PREVIOUS_CALENDAR_V1_SLICE_1_5_FIX_BUNDLE_CONSUMED","line":117},{"title":"../../📤_outbox/_archive/2026-05/445_LATEST_PREVIOUS_CALENDAR_V1_SLICE_1_6_CSS_BUG_FIX_CONSUMED","target":"../../📤_outbox/_archive/2026-05/445_LATEST_PREVIOUS_CALENDAR_V1_SLICE_1_6_CSS_BUG_FIX_CONSUMED","line":118}],"metadata":{"title":"Calendar Feature V1 Spec — Strategic LOCKED 2026-05-12 + Cumulative Drift S1.0→S1.7 LANDED 2026-05-13","type":"concept","status":"locked-v1","locked_date":"2026-05-12","authority":"Daniel CEO strategic input chat ACASĂ 2026-05-12 Calendar V1 spec funcțional + UX states + wireframe placement + Coach role anti-paternalism LOCKED post Cluster G closure milestone + Daniel CEO directive chat ACASĂ 2026-05-13 cumulative Slices S1.0→S1.7 LANDED mockup-only consolidate via /wiki-ingest","voice_preservation":"synthesis + verbatim + bugatti + crossrefs","cross_refs":["[[anti-recurrence-rules]]","[[bugatti-craft]]","[[gigel-test]]","[[andura-suflet]]","[[metoda-hibrida-chat-cc]]","[[../entities/engines/engine-coach-director]]","[[../entities/adrs/adr-024-goal-driven-program-templates]]","[[../entities/adrs/adr-011-coach-decision-log-architecture]]","[[../entities/adrs/adr-020-storage-tiering-strategy]]","[[../entities/adrs/adr-026-offline-coaching-tree]]","[[../summaries/react-migration-roadmap]]"],"amendments":[{"date":"2026-05-12","note":"4-strategic LOCK V1 chat ACASĂ — clarification 1 color-only L-D (NU workout type label per zi) + clarification 2 mid-week zilele trecute raman bifate invariant + restul recalibrate + clarification 3 ZERO warning extremes (1 zi min OK + 7/7 OK anti-paternalism) + clarification 4 NEW augmentat Coach vede bigger picture multi-week NU săptămâna izolată — Engine"},{"date":"2026-05-12","note":"S1.0 mockup design master LANDED commit `6ec01e8` — Calendar L-D 7 cells + 4 UX states baseline + colors SSOT heatmap palette (`#3d7a4a` Greu / `#d4e6cb` Usor / paper-2 neutru) + wireframe placement între coach-reflectie L825 și Obiectiv settings-section L828 (Option 1 placement Daniel-aligned semantic Antrenor home flow today-recommendation → weekly view → goal selector preserved) + mockup replace separat atomic `52be5f6` (325KB ~4400 LOC newer uploaded Daniel verbatim *\"ti-am dat eu mockupul. fa replace. e mai nou\"*)"},{"date":"2026-05-12","note":"S1.5 fix bundle vizual LANDED commit `afc74a5` — 4 mods bundle (🔒 emoji → lucide pencil parity `.nutri-edit-btn` proteine pattern 28×28 + compact padding/radius/title/gap shrink + \"Saptamana ta\" → \"Program de antrenament\" CENTRAT pencil absolute right + demo JS state machine mockup-only `toggleCalendarEdit/Day` + `saveCalendarEdit` parity `editNutri/saveNutri` existing) + Daniel verbatim correction reset artefact title \"pune si tu ceva gen Program de antrenament. Si centreaza textul\""},{"date":"2026-05-12","note":"S1.6 CSS bug fix UX-friction LANDED commit `bc5be41` — root cause CSS rule `.calendar-week[data-state=\"edit\"]:not([data-state=\"editing\"])` forțează cells preset (L/Mi/V) la neutru pre-first-tap; primul tap declanșa tranziția JS `edit → editing` care înlătura regula → populare bruscă retroactivă. Bugatti minimal fix DELETE 1 CSS rule + simplify state machine 4 → 3 states (LOCKED / EDIT / SAVE; `editing` redundant + show current selection EDIT state immediate `#d4e6cb` verde deschis). JS `toggleCalendarDay()` strip line `if (state === 'edit') setAttribute('data-state', 'editing')`. UX intent corect — vede starea curentă editabilă imediat tap pencil (signal \"asta e programul, modifică ce vrei\") NU fresh start reset complet"},{"date":"2026-05-13","note":"S1.7 UX reframe 5-mod bundle LANDED commit `de761f5` (+151 / -21 LOC) — A relocate \"Ceva nu merge\" Antrenor → Cont/Ajutor + DELETE Acces rapid section empty + REMOVE \"Nu am aparat\" option din screen-ceva-nu-merge / B NEW \"Trimite-ne un mesaj\" section Cont/Suport între Contacteaza-ne și FAQ (textarea + btn-brick Trimite + `submitFeedback()` mailto:contact@andura.app pre-completat + empty validation + clear post-send) / C REMOVE \"Aparat lipsa\" chip workout sesiune (2 chips rămân Ocupat + Nu vreau) + strip JS dictionary entries + `applyExAction()` lipsa branch / D NEW `screen-aparate-lipsa` picker permanent 10 echipamente standard gym toggle parity onb-medical (banca-inclinata · banca-plana · bara-halterelor · gantere · aparat-cablu · power-rack · leg-press · aparat-extensii · aparat-tractiuni · banda-elastica) + `wv2-missing-equipment` localStorage Tier 0 persist + `toggleEquipmentMissing()` + `hydrateAparateLipsa()` hooked `goto()` wrapper post-render legacy RO normalize via `validIds` filter / E drill entries Cont/General \"Aparate lipsa\" între Aspect și Setari + workout-preview \"Nu am aparat\" btn-ghost full-width între `#preview-exercise-list` și Coach note. Tests 2914 PASS preserved EXACT. ZERO src/ touched. ZERO main branch"}]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:wiki/concepts/calendar-feature-v1-spec.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1yggrft","at":1778653941384},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05162131,-0.00461416,0.00499404,-0.04605478,-0.05116592,-0.01751461,-0.04758927,0.04445607,0.00406742,0.02749496,0.03094508,-0.00077745,0.07392295,0.0487198,0.03171048,-0.04363585,-0.0286603,0.0080031,-0.00544143,0.02219091,0.08804591,-0.00669036,-0.05216973,-0.0321162,0.0481929,0.01581373,-0.04187454,-0.02448994,-0.0599371,-0.23678486,-0.02836119,0.00653647,-0.00442993,0.00536587,-0.01684927,-0.01505676,0.01702636,0.07687546,-0.07563576,0.04541447,0.02653999,-0.00354123,-0.01307859,-0.05437315,-0.05184946,-0.08370789,-0.06680315,0.04078197,-0.08295555,0.02649591,0.00381411,-0.0519802,-0.03199882,0.044163,0.02784159,0.05353912,0.03535652,0.04333103,-0.00401483,0.07249379,0.06258659,-0.04019598,-0.25357616,0.05258844,-0.03138853,0.00581157,-0.02250559,-0.02846107,0.01124231,0.03954558,-0.00718517,0.00059195,0.03107616,0.01242324,0.07104439,-0.00389384,-0.0051831,-0.01375368,-0.04522967,-0.01837985,-0.00953342,0.00734703,-0.01892896,-0.03562654,0.00155091,0.03447063,0.0342318,-0.03612301,0.04979109,0.00780694,-0.06777406,-0.00345958,0.05069323,0.04801561,-0.06799301,-0.01358027,0.0428698,0.00389483,-0.08883974,0.11847963,-0.03270869,0.02343979,-0.02926447,0.00196087,0.00373562,-0.01470597,0.01559147,-0.13375522,-0.05456569,0.01539035,0.00612086,0.00110867,0.04303971,-0.09295201,0.04054032,0.04900074,0.07458323,0.05255703,0.0534516,0.02975151,0.04050944,-0.0116504,0.10549671,-0.0214468,0.0348338,0.03292776,0.07590335,0.03809859,0.02439899,0.01945953,0.07207576,0.01530599,-0.01933634,0.00786225,0.05879352,-0.01462429,-0.01610953,-0.01433518,0.00542343,-0.03738485,-0.0